        &lt;course_detail&gt;&lt;![CDATA[&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Objective&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hands-on experience with Business Rules to create SLA Definitions&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr /&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Estimated Time To complete&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;hour&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr /&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Knowledge Required&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Business Rules,  SLAs&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Search wiki for required knowledge&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr /&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Test Case&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Currently customer has to create incident OLAs manually for each group they create in their instance. Now they want that whenever they create a new group 5 incident OLAs are created to handle that new group OLAs:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;P1 &amp;amp;lt;group Name&amp;gt; OLA &amp;gt;&amp;gt; for all incidents with Priority &amp;#61; 1  the &amp;amp;lt;group&amp;gt; commitment should be 1 hour&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;P2 &amp;amp;lt;group Name&amp;gt; OLA &amp;gt;&amp;gt; for all incidents with Priority &amp;#61; 2  the &amp;amp;lt;group&amp;gt; commitment should be 4 hours&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;P3 &amp;amp;lt;group Name&amp;gt; OLA &amp;gt;&amp;gt; for all incidents with Priority &amp;#61; 3  the &amp;amp;lt;group&amp;gt; commitment should be 8 hours&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;P4 &amp;amp;lt;group Name&amp;gt; OLA &amp;gt;&amp;gt; for all incidents with Priority &amp;#61; 4  the &amp;amp;lt;group&amp;gt; commitment should be 16  hours&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;P5 &amp;amp;lt;group Name&amp;gt; OLA &amp;gt;&amp;gt; for all incidents with Priority &amp;#61; 5  the &amp;amp;lt;group&amp;gt; commitment should be 16  hours&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Expected result&lt;/em&gt;: when customer creates new Active group then 5 above mentioned OLAs should be created. Name and conditions should be dynamically set (Group Name to be included in Name, group sys_id to be included in Start/Stop conditions).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;Please propose a solution and then implement it.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr /&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Trainee  Instructions&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Trainee should propose the technical design and get approval from Coach before implementing the solution. After approval please implement it in the instance specified by the Coach using separate update set. Perform the unit testing before reporting task as completed to the Coach.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13.333333969116211px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Coach Instructions&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Review the development done and test according the scenarios. Special attention to datetime &amp;#34;Duration&amp;#34; field in SLA Definition amd Start, Pause, Stop conditions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
